<p class="ql-align-center">当时我就震惊了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竟然还有比周一上班更大的打击吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同事只甩给了我一个英文单词</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> “NEW” </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让我慢慢体会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200921/571da0dd64ce443fa42da773b752e031.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这三个字母</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看似随意且漫不经心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但一定是暗示了什么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">难道背后另有玄机？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还好我千辛万苦拿到了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一段绝密视频</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">解开了我的迷惑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">点击视频看N姓大佬身份大公开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=215717256&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">原本以为是枚小萌新</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没想到“新人都是怪物”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">优秀到有些过分了啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> N视频 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 是“视频版广东发布” </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">密集覆盖年轻视频用户</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">立足广东，辐射全国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">目标成为广东权威、中国一流的视频平台</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200921/3797a7393c6d48f0b5b90233f3ad8bbb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么，作为一枚“萌新”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">N视频究竟New在哪儿？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>New在年轻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对“丧”“佛”“玩世不恭”说不</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">勇敢奔跑，追寻真相、梦想和光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200921/f45aa07689aa45e7be2bfc2925d1e8ee.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">95后女孩广州街头唱歌落泪，意外走红吸粉上千万：想开演唱会</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200921/7f4a13c2e5ab47bd84bfe6d0c21e0d25.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">广州海归女硕士辞掉工作，跑去南极大陆做探险员，与企鹅海豹作伴</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200921/8745264a04f14b59a1006b8b5bff9bc5.gif" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">被养鸡耽误的程序员：中大毕业生与鸡为伴，9年研发47项专利</span></img></p>
